name: Crypto Dealer's Story II - 3rd Negative - God and the Herbs
description: God said he had given us all the herbs to use. And we used them! There was one day when Jesus smoked so much that we had to carry him home, and everyone was high. Only John, the craziest of us all, who thought the joint was god, that ended up not helping us. I was the one who took this photo, but at the time they had no idea what I was doing, after all, no one there knew a camera...
